data.description: You won’t want to miss this move-in-ready 4-bedroom home in Beacon Hill! This beautiful 2-story ranch house has been meticulously maintained and has received tons of upgrades including new interior paint, luxury vinyl plank flooring, a dual zone HVAC system, and a new roof within the past few years. Approaching the property you’ll love the mature trees, low maintenance vinyl siding, and the large covered front porch. Not to mention the great curb appeal of the window shutters and brick accent on the porch. Heading inside you’ll find tile floors and a large coat closet in the foyer. Just to the left there is a large family room featuring a woodburning fireplace and lots of natural light. The kitchen offers ample countertop and storage space, a center island, a large pantry (doors currently removed but come with the home), and a stylish tile backsplash. The formal dining room provides plenty of space in addition to the breakfast nook in the kitchen with a built-in bench seat that is perfect for those quick meals. On the main level there is also a half bath and a large separate laundry room. Upstairs there is a full hall bathroom and 3 spacious bedrooms including the master with its own full bathroom. The master bathroom offers a dual sink vanity, a walk-in closet, soaker tub, and a separate tile shower. Not to mention the high vaulted ceilings throughout most of the upper level and matching luxury vinyl plank flooring as the main level. Downstairs is fully finished and includes an additional living space and a large bedroom with its own full bathroom. In the backyard you’ll appreciate the large fully fenced lawn, concrete patio, big storage shed, and a sprinkler system. Other features worth noting are the hi-tech video security system and the home is already equipped with AT&T fiber for insanely fast internet speeds. Don’t miss out on this great opportunity, schedule your tour today!
